Class Account

java.lang.Object
Account
Direct Known Subclasses:
Checking, Credit, Savings
public abstract class Account
extends java.lang.Object
Account class is an abstract class that is the parent of Checking, Savings and Credit classes. It includes getters and setters as well as multiple methods that will work with the main RunBank class and its child classes.
Since:
September 25, 2020
